# Izano, Republic of Dagestan

}}
Izano () is a rural locality (a selo) in Akhvakhsky District, Republic of Dagestan, Russia. The population was 1,212 as of 2010.
Geography
Izano is located on the Izanitlar River, 15&nbsp;km southeast of Karata (the district's administrative centre) by road. Kudiyabroso is the nearest rural locality.
